Scrips (R) for statitical analysis of low and high resolution datasetes metrics
____________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________

(1) ThermalSections_analysis&plot.R
Statitical analysis of 10 minte thermak sections with and without thermal activity
Plotting of figure 2B

(2) soaring&gliding_plot&analyse.R
Statitical analysis of coupled soaring-gliding events.
Plotting figure 3A

(2) time_scales_analysis.R
time-scales analysis and plotting of figure 4A
